### 1. Register
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Hema Tejaswi",
    "email": "hema@test.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### 2. Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "hema@test.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Get Profile
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5YjUyMjc2MGM4YjMzM2NmNWNhOWYyNiIsImlhdCI6MTc3MzY5MzAzMiwiZXhwIjoxNzc2Mjg1MDMyfQ.2HlcFPBmxqmHbdYQE9LjZ45mYvWbuK9Y5Kb1cJ9EUIc
### 4. Add Account
